AppArmor was first used in [[Immunix]] Linux 1998-2003. AppArmor was first made available in SUSE and openSUSE, and was first enabled by default in [[SUSE Linux Enterprise Server]] 10 and in [[openSUSE]] 10.1. AppArmor was first successfully ported/packaged for [[Ubuntu (operating system)|Ubuntu]] in April of 2007. AppArmor comes installed default in Ubuntu 7.10 Gutsy Gibbon, and came as a part of the release of Ubuntu 8.04.
